Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的大醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實沒什麼本領
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己本身連個法術也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻有一項特殊的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人受傷了 想請妳們看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的護士小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次見到真正的南丁格爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳願意的話 今晚用妳那純潔的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 我決不原諒你見異思遷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個傷患耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你滿嘴胡說八道說些什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不是說不要看醫生的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的就是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次看到了女人就什麼都不曉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生他可是個病人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是個善良天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 阿拉瑪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全身都發燙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃醫師 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老毛病又開始作祟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦 要不要緊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十萬火急…趕快讓我住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要住院 我要住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是個人病房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託要有衛浴設備的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉瑪 來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟突然變得好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才在想好不容易能夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟阿拉瑪跟伊娃更親近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你們也來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來看護的囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人住院需要人看護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是理所當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家都是擔心你才來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔心了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我本來是不太想來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想偶爾探探病也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是來探病的 就應該帶束花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者吃的東西來才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有比花跟吃的東西更讓你振奮的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙在這幹什麼 你到底來做什麼的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是真的發自內心在關心親愛的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好吃?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆個在陶醉什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉來眼去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 蒂拉妳在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是情侶在病房裡的一個場景而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是煞風景
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫做煞風景呀 大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休可拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命大概已經所剩無幾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說些什麼呀 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 不能說那麼喪氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…窗外的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當最後一片葉子凋落的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命也將…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事的 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我不是在這陪你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休可拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休可拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一段…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段永恆的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 不可以這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 你好色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親…親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱…洛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾…出…去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們全給我滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那些傢伙只會搗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正無論如何 最礙眼的都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是跟阿拉瑪跟伊娃她們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在感覺怎麼樣啊? 凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒什麼起色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 這可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠痊愈 我需要阿拉瑪的愛來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我得趕緊幫你打針才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然覺得已經好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉瑪小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有尖端恐懼症
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到尖頭的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用大支的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大支的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二、三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支實在太大了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被整得好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊娃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你叫凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 我已經完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是醫師 妳在煩惱些什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我能幫忙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就儘管說 別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你受了那麼重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都沒問題了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…還好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太神奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的恢復能力好強呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得她在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有…大石頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉瑪 拿些冰敷的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…多…冰塊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去拿些溫熱的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二、三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙死人了啦 我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀 完全恢復活力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命力真是旺盛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不允許他拈花惹草
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不能讓他得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是這樣子是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春一定不能留白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就要採取行動才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把阿拉瑪 還有伊娃占為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔 誰先來都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿拉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿拉瑪 我是凱洛特哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我們好好地相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就看我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂…蒂拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小阿拉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛 今天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊談邊聽鞭子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…非常地對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休…休…休可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 你正想亂來是不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我解釋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼都沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院裡要保持安靜才行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事呀 阿拉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有個女孩子告訴我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳找我有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我根本就沒有找妳呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼沒事了 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然妳人都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託妳一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他帶來這裡 好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛\N親愛的 我宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉瑪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生 伊娃醫生找你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 伊娃小姐找我?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉跟休可拉兩個人都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在哥哥那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望沒有造成混亂才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事情了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 那個小子突然鬧肚子痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那就別聚集在這裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快把他送到醫院…去…嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 醫院不就在這附近嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫伊娃的女醫生開的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…說伊…伊娃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不要去伊娃那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的小伊…娃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從白天跟你見面之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡就一直想著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你以後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心就緊跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我可是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘…虜…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛他人到底在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要修理親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉 休可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 她是手術狂?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個伊娃醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是感冒或者是腹痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要動手術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在這附近的人全都怕她怕得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說技術好像不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 現在該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底要幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕你會亂動影響到手術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這傢伙會打麻醉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不必那麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過像凱洛特這樣的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就不麻醉應該也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是不要去救他囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:21:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓凱洛特好好的休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱他的手術成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這種下場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是多塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是故意勾起陳年往事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是再怎麼樣單純的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會有一些不為人知的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如男女之間也必須接受彼此的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能擁有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人擁有更多過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說道這個就想到了正義女神 她也有段過去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是和未來有關 值得誇耀的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆走獵人第十七集 重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛就是力量

